Reasoning: The paper deals with image segmentation and 3D reconstruction of neurons from electron microscopic imagery, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks for error detection and correction tasks suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the application of the framework to connectomics, which is the study of neural connections in the brain, suggests that the paper may also be relevant to graphics (cs.GR).
